/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 737 Tm (The bot shall comply with Upstox and applicable Indian market requirements. As of 30 June) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 723 Tm (2026, Upstox documentation states separate API limits for order APIs and standard APIs.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 709 Tm (Order APIs include place, modify, cancel, multi-order, and GTT operations. Regular algos) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 695 Tm (have lower order API throughput than SEBI-registered algos. Upstox also communicates) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 681 Tm (regulatory requirements such as static IP usage for order placement and algo registration) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 667 Tm (thresholds.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 653 Tm (- The bot shall run from a configured static IP when live order placement is enabled.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 639 Tm (- The bot shall keep live order throughput below the configured Upstox order API limits.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 625 Tm (- The bot shall support an optional X-Algo-Name header only when the user has configured) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 611 Tm (  an approved algo name.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 597 Tm (- The bot shall never bypass OAuth, 2FA, static IP, exchange rules, broker restrictions,) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 583 Tm (  or SEBI requirements.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 569 Tm (- The bot shall default to dry-run mode and require explicit live-trading confirmation.) Tj
