1 0 0 1 54 555 Tm (4. System Overview) Tj
/F1 10 Tf
1 0 0 1 54 536 Tm (The application shall be a C++20 or C++23 command-line/service application using CMake. It) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 522 Tm (shall be portable across Windows and Linux where practical, with Windows as the first target) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 508 Tm (environment.) Tj
/F2 12 Tf
