1 0 0 1 54 422 Tm (- Indicator Library: calculates RSI, moving averages, pivots, divergence, trendlines, and) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 408 Tm (  support/resistance zones.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 394 Tm (- Strategy Engine: runs configured strategy modules and aggregates signals.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 380 Tm (- Exit Engine: monitors holdings and triggers target, manual, trailing, stop-loss, or) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 366 Tm (  strategy exits.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 352 Tm (- Risk Manager: validates every buy and sell decision before an order is queued.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 338 Tm (- Order Dispatcher: single controlled component allowed to place, modify, or cancel) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 324 Tm (  orders.) Tj
